<DOC><DOCNO>WSJ911004-0185</DOCNO><DOCID>911004-0185.</DOCID><HL>   Who's News:   PPG Industries Inc.</HL><DATE>10/04/91</DATE><SO>WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B8</SO><CO>   PPG WNEWS</CO><MS>INDUSTRIAL (IDU)</MS><IN>DIVERSIFIED INDUSTRIAL (IDD)</IN><NS>PERSONNEL ANNOUNCEMENTS, PROMOTIONS, APPOINTMENTS (PER)</NS><RE>NORTH AMERICA (NME)PENNSYLVANIA (PA)UNITED STATES (US)</RE><LP>   PPG INDUSTRIES Inc. (Pittsburgh) -- John J. Horgan, vicepresident of corporate administration, was elected vicepresident and general manager of this maker of glass,chemicals and coatings' fiber glass unit. Mr. Horgan, 49,succeeds Franklin H. Green, who will retire Feb. 1 at age 65.In addition, H. Kennedy Linge, 49-year-old corporate counsel,was named treasurer, succeeding Lawrence M. Call, 49, whoresigned. Frank A. Archinaco, 47, vice president ofautomotive original equipment glass, was named to the newlycreated post of vice president of automotive and aircraftproducts.</LP><TEXT/></DOC>